			ownedPackages[ +match[ 1 ] ] = true;
		}
	} );

	    loaded = 0,
	    steamdb_package = 0,
	    total = freePackages.length,
	    modal = ShowBlockingWaitDialog( 'Executing…',
	    	'Please wait until all requests finish. Ignore all the errors, let it finish.' );
	
	for( ; i < total; i++ )
	{
		steamdb_package = freePackages[ i ];
		
		if( ownedPackages[ steamdb_package ] )
		{
			loaded++;
			continue;
		}
		
		jQuery.post(
			'//store.steampowered.com/checkout/addfreelicense',
			{
				action: 'add_to_cart',
				sessionid: g_sessionID,
				subid: steamdb_package
			}
		).always( function( )
			{
				loaded++;
				
				modal.Dismiss();
				
				if( loaded >= total )
				{
					location.reload();
				}
				else
				{
					modal = ShowBlockingWaitDialog( 'Executing…',
						'Loaded <b>' + loaded + '</b>/' + total + '.' );
				}
			}
		);
